text:
Great shop, prices are always the lowest, express delivery and free: D I choose this store because they have very rich assortment and many promotions. Whenever I'm looking for something I find it on Bax-schop and I'm happy. I recommend to everyone: D
I bought a Sennheiser HD-25 studio headphones, I have not used them yet because they are for a friend's gift but I know it's great equipment, use them Nina Kraviz they must be good: D
